    "slug": "according-to-okonkwo-the-british-via-its-indirect-rule-system-ensured-that-afri-2",
    "texto": "According to Okonkwo, the British via its indirect rule system ensured that Africans saw their native leaders as the demons who betrayed their people. He called it a demonocracy and that was the first time I had seen him become so passionate about issues that affect Africa as a people and continent.",
